- Not yet. Did you pass?

1471
01:26:38,246 --> 01:26:39,748
I don't know.
They'll let me know.

1472
01:26:39,790 --> 01:26:42,501
Now diving
for Grand Lakes University...

1473
01:26:42,542 --> 01:26:44,878
Jason Melon.

1474
01:27:04,564 --> 01:27:06,608
Attaboy, Jason! You did it!

1475
01:27:11,989 --> 01:27:13,031
All right!

1476
01:27:17,828 --> 01:27:20,330
I can't believe it.
We could actually win this.

1477
01:27:20,372 --> 01:27:24,293
Melon's dive has put the Hooters
back in this meet.

1478
01:27:25,794 --> 01:27:27,212
What's the matter?

1479
01:27:28,755 --> 01:27:30,757
You're up next, Chas.

1480
01:27:33,677 --> 01:27:35,762
I have got
a really bad cramp.

1481
01:27:35,804 --> 01:27:38,098
I've been having
really bad cramps all week.

1482
01:27:38,140 --> 01:27:41,435
- It's probably menstrual.
- Screw you, Melon!

1483
01:27:44,104 --> 01:27:48,066
Coach Turnbull,
you got another eligible diver?

1484
01:27:50,485 --> 01:27:51,987
Melon!

1485
01:27:55,324 --> 01:27:59,620
Melon! We need ya!
Get your suit on!

1486
01:27:59,661 --> 01:28:00,787
Go ahead.

1487
01:28:00,829 --> 01:28:02,956
Oh, not a chance.
In the shape I'm in...

1488
01:28:02,998 --> 01:28:05,083
you could donate my body
to science fiction.

1489
01:28:05,167 --> 01:28:07,544
Get your suit on! We need ya!

1490
01:28:07,586 --> 01:28:10,922
Come on, pal.
Show 'em what you got.

1491
01:28:10,964 --> 01:28:13,300
Melon! We need ya!

1492
01:28:18,221 --> 01:28:22,809
Now diving in substitution
for Grand Lakes University...

1493
01:28:22,851 --> 01:28:25,270
Thornton Melon.

1494
01:28:27,147 --> 01:28:29,358
He's on my substitute roster...

1495
01:28:29,399 --> 01:28:31,944
but I don't have it right now.

1496
01:28:31,985 --> 01:28:35,697
But what I'll do is,
first chance I get...

1497
01:28:35,739 --> 01:28:37,282
I'll bring it to you.

1498
01:28:55,676 --> 01:28:58,095
What dive is he gonna do?

1499
01:28:58,136 --> 01:29:01,014
The Triple Lindy.

1500
01:29:01,056 --> 01:29:03,308
Melon! Melon! Melon!

1501
01:29:10,065 --> 01:29:12,651
There will be an additional
springboard installed...

1502
01:29:12,693 --> 01:29:15,529
for Melon's dive,
the Triple Lindy.

1503
01:29:15,570 --> 01:29:18,073
- Is that hard?
- It's impossible.

1504
01:30:41,615 --> 01:30:44,159
Melon! You did it!

1505
01:30:49,081 --> 01:30:50,457
That was great!

1506
01:30:55,045 --> 01:30:59,007
Oh, you were great!
That was incredible!

1507
01:30:59,049 --> 01:31:01,551
I guess there's nothing
you can't do.

1508
01:31:01,593 --> 01:31:03,762
I've got the results
of your exams right here.

1509
01:31:03,804 --> 01:31:04,888
Do I want to hear 'em?

1510
01:31:04,930 --> 01:31:07,516
You passed!
All "Ds" and an "A."

1511
01:31:07,557 --> 01:31:09,601
Who gave me the "A"?

1512
01:31:09,643 --> 01:31:11,937
- I did.
- Oh, yeah?

1513
01:31:11,979 --> 01:31:14,606
I would like to introduce
our speaker today.

1514
01:31:14,648 --> 01:31:16,066
This is the first time...

1515
01:31:16,108 --> 01:31:19,486
in the history
of this fine institution...

1516
01:31:19,528 --> 01:31:22,364
that a freshman
has given this address.

1517
01:31:22,406 --> 01:31:24,992
Mr. Thornton Melon.

1518
01:31:38,046 --> 01:31:39,172
Thank you very much.

1519
01:31:39,214 --> 01:31:41,967
Thank you, Dean Martin,
President Sinclair...

1520
01:31:42,050 --> 01:31:44,511
and members
of the graduating class.

1521
01:31:44,553 --> 01:31:47,389
I have only one thing
to say to you today...

1522
01:31:47,431 --> 01:31:48,807
it's a jungle out there.

1523
01:31:48,849 --> 01:31:51,393
You gotta look out
for number one.

1524
01:31:51,435 --> 01:31:54,229
But don't step in number two.

1525
01:31:55,731 --> 01:31:58,775
And so,
to all you graduates...

1526
01:31:58,817 --> 01:32:02,904
as you go out into the world
my advice to you is...

1527
01:32:02,946 --> 01:32:05,907
don't go!
It's rough out there.

1528
01:32:05,949 --> 01:32:08,910
Move back with your parents.
Let them worry about it.

